// Famous-people dataset for the Solo "Famous folks you missed"
// suggestions panel. Merged from curated picks (colloquial fame)
// + Pantheon HPI dataset (encyclopedic backfill). UTF-8 mojibake
// repaired via ftfy; duplicated-lastname entries re-filed;
// entity-level dedupe normalizes name variants.
//
// Pairs with no entries are omitted; the lookup in
// soloSuggestions.ts handles missing keys via `?? []`.
//
// Sources: Pantheon Project (https://pantheon.world/); Wikipedia
// (CC BY-SA) for article URLs.
// ============================================================

